eu.cqse.check.framework.shallowparser

Interface IShallowParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbapShallowParser, AdaShallowParser, CppShallowParser, CsShallowParser, CStyleShallowParserBase, DelphiShallowParser, FortranShallowParser, Iec61131ShallowParser, JavaScriptShallowParser, JavaShallowParser, MagikShallowParser, MatlabShallowParser, OcamlShallowParser, PlsqlShallowParser, PythonShallowParser, RubyShallowParser, ShallowParserBase, TsqlShallowParser, XtendShallowParser

    public interface IShallowParser
    Interface for a shallow parser. All shallow parsers are sufficiently robust to support parsing even of non-compiling code and arbitrary code snippets.
    Version:
    $Rev: 52657 $
    Author:
    $Author: hummelb $

    • Method Detail

      • parseTopLevel

        List<ShallowEntity> parseTopLevel(List<IToken> tokens)
        Shallow parses the given list of tokens and returns all entities found. The tokens provided are expected to represent an entire top-level element of the language (typically a file).

      • parseFragment

        List<ShallowEntity> parseFragment(List<IToken> tokens)
        Shallow parses the given list of tokens and returns all entities found. The tokens provided may be from an arbitrary contiguous chunk of source code.
